# Repository structure — two-repo GitOps pattern

acme-corp/payments-service          # Source repository
├── src/
├── Dockerfile
├── pom.xml
└── .github/workflows/
    └── ci.yml                      # CI pipeline: test, build, scan, sign, update deploy repo

acme-corp/payments-service-deploy   # Deployment repository (written by CI, read by Argo CD)
├── base/
│   ├── deployment.yaml
│   ├── service.yaml
│   └── kustomization.yaml
└── overlays/
    ├── staging/
    │   └── kustomization.yaml      # Updated by CI: kustomize edit set image ...
    └── production/
        └── kustomization.yaml      # Updated by promotion workflow or manual PR
